goodbye.

19
00:02:00,924 --> 00:02:02,404
We're unlikely to meet again.

20
00:02:06,963 --> 00:02:09,043
If you want to thank me
for saving your life,

21
00:02:09,124 --> 00:02:10,603
promise me two things.

22
00:02:11,723 --> 00:02:12,404
Go ahead.

23
00:02:13,804 --> 00:02:14,763
No matter

24
00:02:15,643 --> 00:02:17,323
who asks about recent events,

25
00:02:17,323 --> 00:02:18,483
never mention me.

26
00:02:19,483 --> 00:02:20,684
I want no more ties

27
00:02:20,684 --> 00:02:22,364
to South Mountain Hunters
or Earth Fiends.

28
00:02:24,483 --> 00:02:25,284
And second?

29
00:02:28,244 --> 00:02:30,163
The South Mountain Hunters have chosen

30
00:02:30,203 --> 00:02:31,524
a difficult yet righteous path.

31
00:02:32,923 --> 00:02:34,524
Though I'm not in a position to judge,

32
00:02:35,323 --> 00:02:36,084
I still hope

33
00:02:36,084 --> 00:02:37,603
you'll keep cooperating with them.

34
00:02:38,364 --> 00:02:39,763
This could be your chance

35
00:02:40,923 --> 00:02:42,443
to avenge your mother

36
00:02:43,323 --> 00:02:44,723
and find your sister.

37
00:02:46,763 --> 00:02:47,923
If you agree,

38
00:02:48,323 --> 00:02:49,524
I can help arrange contact.

39
00:02:51,364 --> 00:02:51,964
Deal.

40
00:03:23,564 --> 00:03:24,284
You actually

41
00:03:24,964 --> 00:03:27,323
do have some redeeming qualities.

42
00:03:31,483 --> 00:03:32,524
After all this time,

43
00:03:33,203 --> 00:03:34,163
it's the highest praise

44
00:03:34,163 --> 00:03:35,524
I've ever gotten from you.

45
00:03:48,284 --> 00:03:49,163
Miss Nie.

46
00:03:51,163 --> 00:03:52,483
You're finally back.

47
00:03:54,004 --> 00:03:54,832
What's for the meal?

48
00:03:55,923 --> 00:03:56,964
Whatever you make is fine.

49
00:03:57,923 --> 00:03:58,603
Let me help.

50
00:03:58,603 --> 00:03:59,163
No need.

51
00:03:59,323 --> 00:04:00,723
I can handle it myself.

52
00:04:35,536 --> 00:04:39,248
(Nie Jiuluo)

53
00:05:36,643 --> 00:05:37,804
The long blade dispels life.

54
00:05:39,044 --> 00:05:40,164
The short one pursues death.

55
00:05:41,364 --> 00:05:42,164
Luo,

56
00:05:44,724 --> 00:05:45,924
with the Life-Death Blade,

57
00:05:47,244 --> 00:05:48,564
you are Mad Blade.

58
00:06:59,203 --> 00:07:01,044
Miss Nie, you should rest.

59
00:07:01,203 --> 00:07:02,963
I'll make soup dumplings quickly.

60
00:07:03,124 --> 00:07:04,244
Let me help.

61
00:07:04,523 --> 00:07:05,724
No need to trouble yourself.

62
00:07:06,484 --> 00:07:08,604
It's okay. I'm just idling anyway.

63
00:07:11,604 --> 00:07:13,724
Weren't you supposed to help Mom?

64
00:07:13,963 --> 00:07:15,484
Why are you crafting alone?

65
00:07:18,883 --> 00:07:20,604
Luo, this is the last one.

66
00:07:20,883 --> 00:07:22,124
We can't waste food.

67
00:07:22,883 --> 00:07:24,564
See how skillful our daughter is.

68
00:07:29,523 --> 00:07:30,523
Keep praising her.

69
00:07:30,523 --> 00:07:31,564
We'll run out of dough.

70
00:07:31,643 --> 00:07:32,564
This is on you.

71
00:07:33,083 --> 00:07:33,843
So what?

72
00:07:34,323 --> 00:07:35,804
We can turn the rest of the filling

73
00:07:36,484 --> 00:07:37,164
into meatballs.

74
00:07:40,604 --> 00:07:41,443
Press here.

75
00:07:43,763 --> 00:07:44,523
Spin faster.

76
00:07:44,523 --> 00:07:45,283
Your method...

77
00:07:46,124 --> 00:07:46,843
isn't working.

78
00:07:52,484 --> 00:07:55,164
You remembered something happy?

79
00:08:02,684 --> 00:08:03,484
Nothing.

80
00:08:04,203 --> 00:08:06,484
Just feels nice like this.

81
00:08:08,484 --> 00:08:09,443
That's good.

82
00:08:10,124 --> 00:08:11,083
Then in the future,

83
00:08:11,083 --> 00:08:12,763
stop wandering off so often.

84
00:08:12,924 --> 00:08:13,763
Come home more.

85
00:08:14,164 --> 00:08:15,484
No place compares to home.

86
00:08:32,283 --> 00:08:33,084
You...

87
00:08:33,163 --> 00:08:34,604
I didn't let you in.

88
00:08:35,643 --> 00:08:36,484
Miss Nie.

89
00:08:39,763 --> 00:08:41,283
It's okay, Ms. Lu. He's my friend.

90
00:08:41,484 --> 00:08:42,163
You can go.

91
00:08:43,364 --> 00:08:44,004
Alright.

92
00:08:48,643 --> 00:08:49,683
Jiang's in trouble.

93
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:16,016
(Massage, Foot Spa, Wellness)

94
00:09:16,016 --> 00:09:18,046
(Nutritious Breakfast)

95
00:09:19,728 --> 00:09:21,084
(Free Checkups)

96
00:09:21,084 --> 00:09:22,923
Keep it dry. Avoid irritants.

97
00:09:22,923 --> 00:09:24,283
I shouldn't need to remind you.

98
00:09:24,403 --> 00:09:26,160
Return in three days
for a dressing change.

99
00:09:26,324 --> 00:09:26,844
Got it.

100
00:09:27,364 --> 00:09:28,923
You're practically a doctor by now.

101
00:09:28,923 --> 00:09:29,883
So no need to return.

102
00:09:30,124 --> 00:09:31,364
Buy gauze and do it yourself.

103
00:09:32,204 --> 00:09:33,283
Say hi to Xiong.

104
00:09:33,563 --> 00:09:34,724
- Okay.
- Okay.

105
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:46,512
(Massage)

106
