What?

107
00:09:59,763 --> 00:10:00,763
Forget something?

108
00:10:03,484 --> 00:10:05,563
Can't you read 'Closed'?

109
00:10:16,163 --> 00:10:19,124
Front shop, back clinic.
This is shady business.

110
00:10:19,883 --> 00:10:21,043
Don't say that.

111
00:10:21,563 --> 00:10:23,043
If the Dragon King needs a jade bed,

112
00:10:23,163 --> 00:10:24,643
Xicang's Wanbao Tower has it.

113
00:10:25,244 --> 00:10:26,324
My dream was to open

114
00:10:26,724 --> 00:10:29,204
an East-meets-West place

115
00:10:30,163 --> 00:10:31,403
where food is medicine.

116
00:10:31,604 --> 00:10:33,444
Whether you're injured

117
00:10:33,444 --> 00:10:34,643
or ill or something,

118
00:10:34,724 --> 00:10:36,244
you can find solutions here.

119
00:10:37,004 --> 00:10:37,964
What about Xiong Hei?

120
00:10:38,403 --> 00:10:39,444
What 'solutions' for them?

121
00:10:41,683 --> 00:10:42,964
Aren't they doing business?

122
00:10:43,964 --> 00:10:45,124
Working in all weathers,

123
00:10:45,244 --> 00:10:46,403
illnesses and ailments

124
00:10:47,043 --> 00:10:47,643
are normal.

125
00:10:50,204 --> 00:10:51,084
Seems like

126
00:10:51,563 --> 00:10:53,643
Ms. Lin hasn't funded
your education or business

127
00:10:53,643 --> 00:10:55,484
entirely for charity.

128
00:10:55,883 --> 00:10:57,163
You apply what you've learned.

129
00:11:02,124 --> 00:11:03,403
Aren't you from Roadsound too?

130
00:11:04,683 --> 00:11:05,364
What?

131
00:11:05,923 --> 00:11:07,763
Are you turning in your own?

132
00:11:10,163 --> 00:11:11,763
Now you accept me as your own?

133
00:11:12,004 --> 00:11:13,803
Weren't you guarding against me earlier?

134
00:11:19,964 --> 00:11:21,124
What do you want?

135
00:11:22,244 --> 00:11:23,124
What's with you?

136
00:11:24,004 --> 00:11:25,324
After all these years, what now?

137
00:11:25,403 --> 00:11:26,923
You came all this way to expose me?

138
00:11:30,403 --> 00:11:32,844
Fine. If you truly consider me your own,

139
00:11:34,604 --> 00:11:35,403
examine me.

140
00:11:41,484 --> 00:11:42,883
I got injured from a hiking fall.

141
00:11:50,964 --> 00:11:53,204
Yes. It doesn't look
like hiking injuries.

142
00:11:53,444 --> 00:11:54,204
No questions.

143
00:11:54,484 --> 00:11:55,724
Just find me a resting place.

144
00:11:59,683 --> 00:12:01,163
It's definitely from hiking.

145
00:12:02,043 --> 00:12:02,923
I can tell.

146
00:12:03,324 --> 00:12:03,923
Stop that.

147
00:12:04,484 --> 00:12:05,124
After you.

148
00:13:23,964 --> 00:13:25,403
Why did you leave Jiang here?

149
00:13:27,563 --> 00:13:28,883
It was urgent,

150
00:13:29,563 --> 00:13:30,803
and he insisted on staying.

151
00:13:31,444 --> 00:13:32,244
So I didn't argue...

152
00:13:32,244 --> 00:13:33,523
But you should've insisted too.

153
00:13:36,364 --> 00:13:37,204
I'm sorry, Luo.

154
00:13:38,043 --> 00:13:39,124
It's my mistake.

155
00:13:56,084 --> 00:13:56,883
If

156
00:13:58,124 --> 00:13:59,283
I had stayed to cover

157
00:14:00,883 --> 00:14:02,244
and gotten captured instead,

158
00:14:05,043 --> 00:14:06,444
would you be blaming Jiang

159
00:14:07,563 --> 00:14:08,683
the way you are now?

160
00:14:47,004 --> 00:14:47,923
Laobanzhang Tea,

161
00:14:48,763 --> 00:14:49,604
an ancient tree tea.

162
00:14:58,484 --> 00:14:59,163
You people

163
00:15:00,563 --> 00:15:01,364
know tea?

164
00:15:02,724 --> 00:15:04,403
With millennia of tea culture,

165
00:15:04,763 --> 00:15:07,004
we newcomers wouldn't claim expertise.

166
00:15:08,084 --> 00:15:09,604
Yet you presume mastery.

167
00:15:10,124 --> 00:15:11,444
With history merely a blink

168
00:15:11,643 --> 00:15:14,004
in the eyes of heaven and earth,

169
00:15:14,724 --> 00:15:17,124
how dare you pose as nature's overlords?

170
00:15:20,844 --> 00:15:22,803
Arrogance didn't bring humanity

171
00:15:22,803 --> 00:15:23,844
to its current state.

172
00:15:25,283 --> 00:15:27,364
Most of our progress

173
00:15:27,763 --> 00:15:30,803
comes from exploration, curiosity,

174
00:15:31,004 --> 00:15:32,283
and constant error correction,

175
00:15:32,283 --> 00:15:32,844
and yes,

176
00:15:34,324 --> 00:15:35,283
some luck.

177
00:15:36,324 --> 00:15:37,964
That's how we've achieved this.

178
00:15:38,364 --> 00:15:39,484
If you just imitate us

179
00:15:39,763 --> 00:15:42,964
without understanding,

180
00:15:44,563 --> 00:15:46,204
you'll stumble through endless detours.

181
00:15:48,523 --> 00:15:51,724
So how did
the South Mountain Hunters decline

182
00:15:52,124 --> 00:15:53,004
to this state?

183
00:15:53,844 --> 00:15:54,604
Underestimation?

184
00:15:55,364 --> 00:15:56,043
Complacency?

185
00:15:56,084 --> 00:15:57,283
Or fractured organization?

186
00:16:01,324 --> 00:16:03,643
Once the Blade, Hound, and Whip clans

187
00:16:03,643 --> 00:16:05,563
worked seamlessly together.

188
00:16:05,964 --> 00:16:08,324
Yet this time,

189
00:16:09,004 --> 00:16:11,124
only Mad Dog fought seriously.

190
00:16:12,364 --> 00:16:15,444
When will we see the Whip Clan

191
00:16:16,523 --> 00:16:17,883
and Blade Clan's prowess?

192
00:16:25,643 --> 00:16:26,683
Do you feel sorry?

193
00:16:31,724 --> 00:16:33,004
I'd say

194
00:16:33,484 --> 00:16:34,803
you should be grateful.

195
00:16:35,803 --> 00:16:38,324
Had you encountered all three,
Ghost Whip,

196
00:16:38,844 --> 00:16:39,523
Mad Dog,

197
00:16:40,043 --> 00:16:40,883
and Mad Blade,

198
00:16:41,964 --> 00:16:43,484
you wouldn't live to see the sun.

199
00:16:43,604 --> 00:16:44,724
No need to summon them.

200
00:16:45,283 --> 00:16:47,004
I'll visit them myself.

201
00:16:47,163 --> 00:16:49,244
So Mr. Jiang,

202
00:16:49,883 --> 00:16:52,283
please reveal Mad Blade's identity.

203
00:16:53,643 --> 00:16:55,084
Or you won't live to see

204
00:16:55,084 --> 00:16:56,604
tonight's moon.

205
00:17:00,084 --> 00:17:02,163
So this tea meeting is about this?

206
00:17:03,043 --> 00:17:04,123
Should've said so earlier.

207
00:17:06,523 --> 00:17:08,283
Our generation's Mad Blade
was Old Blade.

208
00:17:08,884 --> 00:17:10,323
You've already fought him.

209
00:17:12,164 --> 00:17:12,684
He was

210
00:17:13,884 --> 00:17:15,123
badly wounded by him.

211
00:17:18,763 --> 00:17:19,404
Old Blade!

212
00:17:54,083 --> 00:17:54,884
Sir?

213
00:17:54,884 --> 00:17:56,204
What's happening, sir?

214
00:17:57,164 --> 00:17:58,083
Where are we going?

215
00:18:00,323 --> 00:18:01,004
Sir?

216
00:18:04,523 --> 00:18:05,204
Jiang?

217
00:18:07,724 --> 00:18:08,523
You ask me?

218
00:18:09,244 --> 00:18:10,924
I should be questioning you.

219
00:18:11,884 --> 00:18:13,283
Will you rescue me

220
00:18:14,283 --> 00:18:15,283
and my brothers or not?

221
00:18:31,843 --> 00:18:34,843
Jiang! Jiang!

222
00:18:38,164 --> 00:18:38,884
Jiang!

223
00:18:52,404 --> 00:18:53,484
Sir,

224
00:18:54,363 --> 00:18:55,843
I want to change the destination.

225
00:18:56,043 --> 00:18:57,884
The meter's running. It's up to you.

226
00:18:59,724 --> 00:19:01,924
I'm going to South Mountain.
It might be a bit far.

227
00:19:03,363 --> 00:19:05,283
Anywhere within the province is fine.

228
00:19:14,444 --> 00:19:15,964
You risked your life

229
00:19:15,964 --> 00:19:17,884
covering your team's retreat.

230
00:19:18,244 --> 00:19:19,964
Now you're suddenly being candid?

231
00:19:20,763 --> 00:19:21,843
How can I trust you?

232
00:19:39,244 --> 00:19:39,924
I

233
00:19:42,763 --> 00:19:44,004
am in your custody now.

234
00:19:44,964 --> 00:19:46,684
And we've lost Mad Blade
as our trump card.

235
00:19:47,204 --> 00:19:49,603
There's no reason for me
to bluff with you.

236
00:19:55,644 --> 00:19:56,444
Maybe...

237
00:19:57,843 --> 00:19:59,444
maybe it's just as you said.

238
00:20:00,563 --> 00:20:02,644
The South Mountain Hunters
declined to this state

239
00:20:03,083 --> 00:20:04,843
because of underestimation, complacency,

240
00:20:06,283 --> 00:20:07,563
and fractured organization.

241
00:20:10,964 --> 00:20:12,283
Moreover, my candor

242
00:20:12,644 --> 00:20:15,123
is meant to secure
my companions' freedom.

243
00:20:19,244 --> 00:20:21,123
They have their own lives to live.

244
00:20:21,884 --> 00:20:23,523
For them, being South Mountain Hunters

245
00:20:24,123 --> 00:20:25,404
is just a job,

246
00:20:26,283 --> 00:20:27,204
not a calling.

247
00:20:42,352 --> 00:20:45,712
(Rare Stone Garden)

248
00:20:51,244 --> 00:20:53,523
I haven't seen Yan Tuo
these past few days.

249
00:21:00,083 --> 00:21:00,763
"Xiong,

250
00:21:01,204 --> 00:21:03,363
I met this girl recently.

251
00:21:03,644 --> 00:21:04,684
Feisty one.

252
00:21:05,043 --> 00:21:06,964
I'm taking her hiking
for a couple of days.

253
00:21:07,523 --> 00:21:08,924
If Ms. Lin asks,

254
00:21:09,043 --> 00:21:10,523
cover for me.

255
00:21:10,724 --> 00:21:12,363
