256
00:21:17,968 --> 00:21:20,194
(Design of a Bionic Fire-Fighting Robot)

257
00:21:20,624 --> 00:21:26,832
(Xicang's Nanshan Rescue Team's
Charity Efforts)

258
00:21:34,043 --> 00:21:36,323
First Mrs. Hua was seriously injured.

259
00:21:37,004 --> 00:21:38,404
Then Mr. Crip.

260
00:21:41,884 --> 00:21:44,043
Now even Jiang's been captured.

261
00:21:44,444 --> 00:21:45,803
South Mountain Hunters?

262
00:21:47,204 --> 00:21:48,563
More like South Mountain prey.

263
00:21:50,523 --> 00:21:51,884
Enough talk.

264
00:21:54,283 --> 00:21:56,204
I'll pull seniority to speak first.

265
00:21:57,244 --> 00:21:58,363
With Baichuan gone,

266
00:21:58,363 --> 00:21:59,644
we can't remain leaderless.

267
00:22:00,164 --> 00:22:01,164
The priority

268
00:22:01,444 --> 00:22:02,724
is finding someone to lead.

269
00:22:03,603 --> 00:22:04,444
That should be you.

270
00:22:04,724 --> 00:22:06,283
You're the most senior and respected.

271
00:22:06,724 --> 00:22:07,444
Right, Mr. Crip.

272
00:22:07,924 --> 00:22:08,884
You should lead us.

273
00:22:09,083 --> 00:22:10,043
We'd all follow.

274
00:22:11,164 --> 00:22:12,244
If I lead,

275
00:22:12,684 --> 00:22:14,323
I won't let us be humiliated like this.

276
00:22:14,644 --> 00:22:16,204
Those inhuman beings,

277
00:22:16,204 --> 00:22:17,283
every last one of them,

278
00:22:17,644 --> 00:22:18,684
will be wiped out.

279
00:22:18,724 --> 00:22:19,924
We'll rescue Baichuan.

280
00:22:20,123 --> 00:22:22,043
- Great!
- Great!

281
00:22:24,603 --> 00:22:25,204
Great?

282
00:22:27,244 --> 00:22:28,763
Who attacked us?

283
00:22:29,724 --> 00:22:30,603
Who are they?

284
00:22:30,684 --> 00:22:31,484
Where are they now?

285
00:22:31,523 --> 00:22:32,244
Do you know?

