And

287
00:22:34,563 --> 00:22:36,363
which direction should we investigate?

288
00:22:43,843 --> 00:22:45,004
At my age,

289
00:22:46,004 --> 00:22:47,803
I know my limitations.

290
00:22:48,603 --> 00:22:50,684
I'm more temper than talent.

291
00:22:51,404 --> 00:22:52,363
In real crises,

292
00:22:52,724 --> 00:22:55,283
I might not stay calm
like you youngsters.

293
00:22:56,083 --> 00:22:57,363
So I can't lead.

294
00:22:58,964 --> 00:23:00,123
But if you

295
00:23:00,244 --> 00:23:01,803
truly respect me as your elder,

296
00:23:03,083 --> 00:23:04,004
I'll name someone.

297
00:23:19,563 --> 00:23:20,484
Xing Shen

298
00:23:20,884 --> 00:23:22,283
has lived here for years

299
00:23:23,603 --> 00:23:25,603
and knows South Mountain
better than any of us.

300
00:23:26,363 --> 00:23:27,843
I watched him grow up.

301
00:23:28,444 --> 00:23:29,563
Everything he does

302
00:23:30,004 --> 00:23:32,004
prioritizes the Hunters' interests

303
00:23:32,004 --> 00:23:33,004
above all else.

304
00:23:34,724 --> 00:23:36,763
With Mad Blade and Ghost Whip gone,

305
00:23:37,563 --> 00:23:39,563
Mad Dog should naturally lead.

306
00:23:41,204 --> 00:23:43,004
Someone who kept an Earth Fiend
leading us?

307
00:23:43,724 --> 00:23:45,283
It's like a rat among the cats' ranks.

308
00:23:45,763 --> 00:23:46,763
I don't know about you,

309
00:23:47,083 --> 00:23:48,083
but this disgusts me.

310
00:23:48,484 --> 00:23:49,323
About that matter,

311
00:23:49,484 --> 00:23:51,043
Jiang already concluded it

312
00:23:51,043 --> 00:23:52,164
with proper resolution.

313
00:23:52,843 --> 00:23:55,043
Hadn't that Earth Fiend
appeared that day,

314
00:23:55,563 --> 00:23:56,803
disrupting the enemy's plans,

315
00:23:57,244 --> 00:23:58,724
we'd have suffered heavier losses.

316
00:23:58,843 --> 00:24:00,244
Since when did that fiend help?

317
00:24:00,323 --> 00:24:00,884
Exactly.

318
00:24:00,884 --> 00:24:01,644
I think...

319
00:24:02,404 --> 00:24:03,603
We need long-term planning.

320
00:24:03,603 --> 00:24:04,924
Enough arguing.

321
00:24:12,884 --> 00:24:13,843
Let's vote then.

322
00:24:16,523 --> 00:24:19,603
I agree Xing Shen
should lead temporarily.

323
00:24:20,004 --> 00:24:20,884
Show of hands.

324
00:24:37,843 --> 00:24:39,763
Shen will help us all.

325
00:24:41,763 --> 00:24:43,204
Ma trusts him.

326
00:24:43,644 --> 00:24:44,803
Ma trusts in Shen.

327
00:24:47,123 --> 00:24:47,924
In the past,

328
00:24:49,724 --> 00:24:51,803
Mom trusted Shen too.

329
00:25:18,724 --> 00:25:21,404
The ink line on wood becomes the rule.

330
00:25:21,924 --> 00:25:22,964
It's majority support.

331
00:25:23,323 --> 00:25:23,803
Done.

332
00:25:28,004 --> 00:25:29,484
South Mountain is in your hands now.

333
00:25:33,644 --> 00:25:34,803
Don't let me down.

334
00:26:09,043 --> 00:26:10,404
Thank you for your trust.

335
00:26:11,244 --> 00:26:12,323
I'll

336
00:26:13,363 --> 00:26:15,484
temporarily take Jiang's position.

337
00:26:16,043 --> 00:26:18,603
I've contacted Ghost Whip and Mad Blade.

338
00:26:19,404 --> 00:26:21,043
They've confirmed participation.

339
00:26:22,724 --> 00:26:24,444
With unity,

340
00:26:24,803 --> 00:26:26,803
we'll rescue Jiang quickly.

341
00:26:27,763 --> 00:26:28,724
Ghost Whip is one thing,

342
00:26:28,724 --> 00:26:29,444
but Mad Blade

343
00:26:30,164 --> 00:26:32,484
was difficult even when Jiang led us.

344
00:26:33,004 --> 00:26:33,964
Will she come?

345
00:26:35,043 --> 00:26:35,644
Right.

346
00:26:39,244 --> 00:26:40,004
She will.

347
00:26:45,763 --> 00:26:46,763
It's fine.

348
00:26:47,004 --> 00:26:48,123
Don't worry.

349
00:26:49,603 --> 00:26:51,083
You've worked hard these years.

350
00:26:52,283 --> 00:26:53,404
Spend time with family.

351
00:26:54,724 --> 00:26:55,924
In these peaceful times,

352
00:26:56,004 --> 00:26:57,123
what could go wrong?

353
00:26:57,323 --> 00:26:57,924
Right?

354
00:26:58,323 --> 00:26:59,484
Even if trouble comes,

355
00:26:59,724 --> 00:27:01,964
Banya Mountain and Qiaotou Gully

356
00:27:02,444 --> 00:27:04,603
have sent reinforcements recently.

357
00:27:05,803 --> 00:27:07,603
You just rest another fortnight.

358
00:27:08,123 --> 00:27:08,964
We got this.

359
00:27:10,763 --> 00:27:11,803
No need.

360
00:27:12,724 --> 00:27:14,684
I just check on the mountains
once in a while.

361
00:27:15,563 --> 00:27:16,363
Stop worrying.

362
00:27:18,603 --> 00:27:19,843
Alright, it's settled then.

363
00:27:20,004 --> 00:27:20,603
I need to go.

364
00:27:25,523 --> 00:27:27,164
Why not recruit your team

365
00:27:27,563 --> 00:27:28,884
to join us?

366
00:27:29,924 --> 00:27:31,523
At least we'd look formidable.

367
00:27:32,123 --> 00:27:33,444
Might scare others.

368
00:27:38,363 --> 00:27:39,684
Can't even shut you up with food?

369
00:27:41,964 --> 00:27:43,763
'Peaceful times'?

370
00:27:44,444 --> 00:27:45,123
What's wrong?

371
00:27:45,283 --> 00:27:47,083
Having food is peace.

372
00:27:48,763 --> 00:27:50,763
But some can't eat anymore.

373
00:27:51,884 --> 00:27:53,843
Sun Zhou is starving himself.

374
00:27:54,763 --> 00:27:55,283
Really?

375
00:27:57,043 --> 00:27:58,083
He's been refusing meals,

376
00:27:58,083 --> 00:28:00,004
saying cooked food disgusts him.

377
00:28:00,283 --> 00:28:01,763
I think it's time.

378
00:28:04,043 --> 00:28:05,763
I need to check on him.

379
00:28:06,244 --> 00:28:07,763
We already have one Earth Fiend.

380
00:28:07,924 --> 00:28:10,004
Can't handle another biter.

381
00:29:14,644 --> 00:29:15,444
Today,

382
00:29:19,283 --> 00:29:20,363
I spoke harshly.

383
00:29:20,363 --> 00:29:22,083
I should've stayed behind

384
00:29:23,404 --> 00:29:25,323
instead of letting Jiang take the risk.

385
00:29:31,803 --> 00:29:33,164
No one expected

386
00:29:33,684 --> 00:29:34,763
that situation.

387
00:29:35,283 --> 00:29:36,244
It's not your fault.

388
00:29:38,884 --> 00:29:40,083
Besides apologizing,

389
00:29:41,164 --> 00:29:42,323
I want to say

390
00:29:43,684 --> 00:29:44,724
I have a friend

391
00:29:45,484 --> 00:29:47,164
who might help rescue Jiang.

392
00:29:48,283 --> 00:29:49,083
But

393
00:29:50,924 --> 00:29:52,004
it's risky.

394
00:29:54,164 --> 00:29:54,843
A friend?

395
00:29:56,004 --> 00:29:57,244
Sun Zhou's gone!

396
00:29:57,684 --> 00:29:58,924
Sun Zhou's gone!

397
00:30:21,484 --> 00:30:22,484
All this time,

398
00:30:22,684 --> 00:30:23,924
Sun Zhou has been locked up?

399
00:30:26,563 --> 00:30:28,283
He has red threads through his pupils.

400
00:30:29,523 --> 00:30:31,404
We should've sent him to Golden Gate,

401
00:30:32,123 --> 00:30:33,603
but Jiang stopped us.

402
00:30:38,563 --> 00:30:40,924
I begged Jiang to save him.

403
00:30:45,444 --> 00:30:46,884
You're too softhearted.

404
00:30:48,523 --> 00:30:50,043
It's South Mountain Hunters' duty

405
00:30:50,404 --> 00:30:51,563
to protect civilians

406
00:30:51,563 --> 00:30:52,684
from Earth Fiends.

407
00:30:53,363 --> 00:30:54,523
How's that softhearted?

408
00:30:58,083 --> 00:31:00,043
We called you 'Nine Oxen' as kids.

409
00:31:00,763 --> 00:31:01,523
Do you remember?

410
00:31:06,803 --> 00:31:07,803
I'd forgotten.

411
00:31:09,563 --> 00:31:10,684
Jiang said

412
00:31:11,444 --> 00:31:13,004
you seem obedient,

413
00:31:14,283 --> 00:31:15,603
yet stand firmest.

414
00:31:17,043 --> 00:31:18,004
Not even nine oxen

415
00:31:19,363 --> 00:31:20,684
can turn you from your course.

416
00:31:23,563 --> 00:31:24,404
If we delay,

417
00:31:24,684 --> 00:31:26,043
even nine horses won't catch him.

418
00:31:26,644 --> 00:31:27,244
Sit tight.

419
00:31:35,843 --> 00:31:37,323
How'd you track Sun Zhou?

420
00:31:37,644 --> 00:31:38,924
He stole Big Head's phone

421
00:31:38,924 --> 00:31:40,244
while escaping.

422
00:31:41,164 --> 00:31:42,244
It has GPS.

423
00:31:43,763 --> 00:31:45,523
Jiang's phone doesn't?

424
00:31:47,123 --> 00:31:48,363
Big Head uses the rescue team's

425
00:31:48,363 --> 00:31:49,684
dedicated tracking system.

426
00:31:54,123 --> 00:31:55,404
Maybe we didn't need it before.

427
00:31:56,684 --> 00:31:58,843
Let's get everyone equipped
in the future.

428
00:32:03,083 --> 00:32:04,404
Given his movement speed,

429
00:32:04,803 --> 00:32:05,763
let's go faster.

430
00:32:34,123 --> 00:32:35,043
I'm back.

431
00:32:37,644 --> 00:32:38,763
It's too remote here.

432
00:32:39,283 --> 00:32:40,563
This was all I could get.

433
00:32:41,244 --> 00:32:43,644
Make do with this for now.

434
00:32:48,523 --> 00:32:49,244
(Cang Water)
Have some water.

435
00:32:55,924 --> 00:32:56,724
What are you doing?

436
00:33:05,523 --> 00:33:06,484
Are you in trouble?

437
00:33:07,563 --> 00:33:10,444
You came alone to this wilderness,

438
00:33:11,484 --> 00:33:13,404
saying you were hiding at your uncle's.

439
00:33:19,204 --> 00:33:20,283
Let me go.

440
00:33:21,563 --> 00:33:22,684
I'll get mad.

441
00:33:42,244 --> 00:33:43,204
Let me go.

442
00:34:36,243 --> 00:34:38,163
She's fine, no bites.

443
00:34:38,243 --> 00:34:39,312
I'll get her to hospital.

444
00:34:40,844 --> 00:34:42,163
I'll take Sun Zhou back then.

445
00:34:43,804 --> 00:34:45,523
He's innocent.
He just got dragged into it.

446
00:34:46,243 --> 00:34:47,163
Try to help him.

447
00:34:50,083 --> 00:34:50,844
I will.

448
00:36:43,964 --> 00:36:45,924
(Nie Jiuluo: 9:00, Spring Return Road)

449
00:36:51,203 --> 00:36:54,243
(Just saw it. On my way now,)

450
00:36:54,243 --> 00:36:56,563
(but I'll be a few minutes late.)

451
00:37:08,804 --> 00:37:09,643
Miss Nie,

452
00:37:09,643 --> 00:37:11,083
breakfast will be ready soon.

453
00:37:12,163 --> 00:37:12,884
Miss Nie?

454
00:37:13,243 --> 00:37:14,203
Ms. Lu, you have it.

455
00:37:14,203 --> 00:37:15,163
I need to go out.

456
00:37:15,324 --> 00:37:17,083
Leaving again right after coming back?

457
00:37:18,364 --> 00:37:20,043
Don't young people today ever sleep?

458
00:37:35,444 --> 00:37:36,203
He left so early?

459
00:37:38,444 --> 00:37:39,764
Do you want me to call and check?

460
00:37:41,804 --> 00:37:42,924
Leave him for now.

461
00:38:15,324 --> 00:38:17,683
No beating around the bush today, okay?

462
00:38:22,563 --> 00:38:23,404
You look exhausted.

463
00:38:23,643 --> 00:38:25,004
Skip the formalities too.

464
00:38:25,364 --> 00:38:26,203
No small talk.

465
00:38:27,484 --> 00:38:28,563
Alright, go ahead.

466
00:38:31,563 --> 00:38:34,284
Someone named Jiang Baichuan
was captured by Lin Xirou.

467
00:38:35,203 --> 00:38:37,043
He's crucial
to the South Mountain Hunters.

468
00:38:37,404 --> 00:38:38,723
And to me too.

469
00:38:39,643 --> 00:38:41,123
I hope you can help me rescue him.

470
00:38:41,924 --> 00:38:42,523
Of course,

471
00:38:42,523 --> 00:38:43,884
you might not be able to help.

472
00:38:43,884 --> 00:38:45,163
Okay, I'll help you.

473
00:38:46,683 --> 00:38:47,364
You will?

474
00:38:48,683 --> 00:38:49,444
So straightforward?

475
00:38:50,563 --> 00:38:51,563
Wasn't it you who said,

476
00:38:51,563 --> 00:38:53,123
'No beating around the bush'?

477
00:38:56,683 --> 00:38:57,683
I did say that.

478
00:38:57,924 --> 00:38:59,203
But you didn't ask anything.

479
00:38:59,804 --> 00:39:00,683
Isn't that rash?

480
00:39:02,324 --> 00:39:03,484
You contacted me proactively.

481
00:39:03,563 --> 00:39:05,404
It shows the situation is urgent.

482
00:39:06,404 --> 00:39:07,964
You asked me for help.

483
00:39:07,964 --> 00:39:10,203
It means he's very important to you.

484
00:39:10,404 --> 00:39:11,844
If I help with this,

485
00:39:12,243 --> 00:39:13,364
at least I'll gain a chance

486
00:39:13,364 --> 00:39:14,404
to ask for your help.

487
00:39:15,804 --> 00:39:17,404
Moreover, if I successfully rescue him,

488
00:39:17,404 --> 00:39:19,364
you'll owe me a huge favor.

489
00:39:19,444 --> 00:39:20,484
Therefore,

490
00:39:20,484 --> 00:39:22,563
helping you
is my best option either way.

491
00:39:23,123 --> 00:39:24,444
Still think I'm being rash now?

492
00:39:25,203 --> 00:39:26,563
I won't owe you favors.

493
00:39:26,804 --> 00:39:27,683
I'll pay you.

494
00:39:34,163 --> 00:39:34,603
Wait,

495
00:39:35,083 --> 00:39:36,563
I'm helping you with a huge favor.

496
00:39:36,563 --> 00:39:37,804
And you brush me off with this?

497
00:39:59,664 --> 00:40:08,312
♪Your past shines brightly,
your path ahead wide and open♪

498
00:40:14,064 --> 00:40:15,360
When I trained as a kid,

499
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:18,360
Mr. Crip always said,

500
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:20,720
"Own your mistakes.

501
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,320
Stand straight when punished."

502
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:26,120
Same goes for you.

503
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:29,760
Once you enter South Mountain,

504
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:32,160
you'll follow our rules.

505
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:36,440
I don't know how long you'll stay here.

506
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:40,960
I've tried my best.

507
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:47,320
If the Hunters still reject you,

508
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:50,800
there's nothing else I can do.

509
00:40:54,288 --> 00:40:58,488
♪Ripping apart the hidden truth
beneath the surface♪

510
00:40:58,488 --> 00:41:02,848
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
drown this stubborn flame♪

511
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:10,688
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

512
00:41:13,240 --> 00:41:14,000
Don't blame me,

513
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:17,360
Locust.

514
00:41:30,208 --> 00:41:34,568
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

515
00:41:34,568 --> 00:41:38,888
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

516
00:41:38,888 --> 00:41:43,328
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

517
00:41:43,328 --> 00:41:45,768
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

518
00:41:45,768 --> 00:41:49,848
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

519
00:41:49,848 --> 00:41:54,208
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

520
00:41:54,208 --> 00:41:58,568
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

521
00:41:58,568 --> 00:42:02,928
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

522
00:42:02,928 --> 00:42:07,288
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

523
00:42:07,288 --> 00:42:11,568
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

524
00:42:11,568 --> 00:42:16,128
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

525
00:42:16,128 --> 00:42:23,848
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

